org.jasig.portlet.courseschedule.model

Class CourseMeeting

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.portlet.courseschedule.model.CourseMeeting
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<CourseMeeting>

    public class CourseMeeting
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<CourseMeeting>
    CourseMeeting represents a regularly occurring course event. Course meetings are represented as generic, repeating weekly meeting and do not contain timezone information.
    Version:
    $Revision: 20844 $
    Author:
    Jen Bourey, jbourey@unicon.net
